  lines:
  - text: "Hello and welcome on The Bishop's Aide ! \r"
    questionTuto: 0
  - text: "My name is <b>Bertrand de Goth</b>, bishop of Comminges from 1294 to 1299.\r\nContrary
      to what you may think, <b>I am not Saint Bertrand</b>. He is one of my predecessors:
      <b>Bertrand de l\u2019Isle</b> who was bishop here from 1073 to 1123."
    questionTuto: 0
  - text: "One of my missions is to elevate the city of Saint Bertrand de Comminges
      to the rank of <b>pilgrim city </b>with a strong influence around. \r\n<b>And
      to this end, I need your help! \r</b>"
    questionTuto: 0
  - text: "Complete the Era\u2019s <b>objectives by recruiting characters </b>with
      interesting profiles benefitting the city in the crowd of pilgrims entering
      it. \r\nDiscover <b>Saint Bertrand de Comminges\u2019 history </b>from the
      13th to the 15th centuries. "
    questionTuto: 0
  - text: "Do you want to play the tutorial? \r\n<i>(Playing the tutorial is highly
      recommended for a first try)\r</i>"
